title: Newly Renovated Durham Apartment Homes - Open Weekends For Tour !!!
posting_body: ['The Durham features just the right blend of charm and the ideal location for your next home.', 'Our community offers a variety of spacious apartment homes ranging from one-bedroom to three-bedroom floor plans.', 'Residents enjoy breathtaking views from our balconies, generous closet space, quartz counters, plank flooring and much, much more!', 'The Durham is nestled in the suburb of Edina with easy access to several major highways.', '-The Board Room is Perfect for Private Meetings', '-Pet Friendly Featuring Pet Spa and Bark Park', '-Quality-crafted cabinetry with under cabinet lighting', '-The Cinema Offers Cozy Seating for Private Viewing Parties', '-The Patio Offerings a Peaceful Outdoor Lounging Space, Accented with Four Gas Grills and a Gas Fire Pit', '-Spacious, walk-in closets in select apartment homes', '-Brushed stainless kitchen faucet with pull-down sprayer', '-Package Concierge Offering 24-Hour Access to Packages', '-Dedicated Laundry Facilities with High Efficiency Equipment and Onsite Dry Cleaning', '-Moen Align bathroom collection in a chrome finish for a modern look', '-Studio+ Highlighting Wellbeats!', 'Offering a Variety of On-Demand Exercise Programs', '-Walk in showers in select two and three bedroom apartments', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
